:05:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解要信爆煲呢又<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為郭文貴</blockquote><br />\nWFC?</blockquote><br />\n總之就信佢啦</blockquote><br />\nOn9? <br />\n佢講就要信？"},{"pid":"e4d298e21cbe9b2192e533435e9bd0c443ed1033","tid":296720,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T10:15:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d45296e317fbbba0967a01470607ce6ae474ae","tid":296720,"uid":2613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T10:49:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>繼續升玩死重多人喎</blockquote><br />\n大升再大爆煲先玩死最多人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n玩死有錢人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係有錢人多定窮人多？</blockquote><br />\n有好多普通人家一早有樓，升對佢地嚟講一啲影響都無</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n普通人家自住嘅跌先係冇影響<br />\n升嘅話就物價都會升 你諗清楚未？</blockquote><br />\n樓市爆先大鑊<br />\n好多人身家蒸發<br />\n包括大老闆<br />\n無錢咁點？<br />\n炒人囉 咁岩炒左果個供緊樓</blockquote><br />\n好多低能仔明明經歷過97沙士，仲如在夢中唔知樓市爆煲會發生咩事</blockquote><br />\n失業率GOGOGO"},{"pid":"42abca5da735f1e89228468f56488826e9ecd05e","tid":296720,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T10:59:07.000Z","msg":"唔會爆 需求咁大 d人又死都要買"},{"pid":"51407b0bf577d055064c46b2df1421de1886ad2a","tid":296720,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T11:05:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n大升再大爆煲先玩死最多人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n玩死有錢人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係有錢人多定窮人多？</blockquote><br />\n有好多普通人家一早有樓，升對佢地嚟講一啲影響都無</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n普通人家自住嘅跌先係冇影響<br />\n升嘅話就物價都會升 你諗清楚未？</blockquote><br />\n樓市爆先大鑊<br />\n好多人身家蒸發<br />\n包括大老闆<br />\n無錢咁點？<br />\n炒人囉 咁岩炒左果個供緊樓</blockquote><br />\n好多低能仔明明經歷過97沙士，仲如在夢中唔知樓市爆煲會發生咩事</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/a